import React from 'react';
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom';

function Navbar() {
  return (
    <nav className="navbar fixed-top navbar-dark bg-primary">
      <NavLink
        exact
        activeClassName="navbar__link--active"
        className="navbar__link"
        to="/"
      >
        Home
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink
        activeClassName="navbar__link--active"
        className="navbar__link"
        to="/contact-us"
      >
        Contact Us
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink
        activeClassName="navbar__link--active"
        className="navbar__link"
        to="/about-our-center"
      >
        About Our Center
      </NavLink>
    </nav>
  );
}

export default Navbar;
